	<div style="text-align:right;">
		SOUZA, Jeferson Dos Santos de<sup>1</sup>; ALVES, Wagner Sabino Lourenço<sup>2</sup>; KOZLOWSKI, Luiz Alberto<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
